[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1041","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1041.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1325","title":"SAS System 5.18 for VAX/VMS 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SAS System 5.18 for VAX/VMS 存在不安全的目录和启动文件权限配置漏洞。由于系统安装时未正确设置目录及启动文件的访问权限，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞修改或替换关键文件，从而获取更高权限。该漏洞影响 SAS System 5.18 版本，攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议用户升级至修复版本或手动调整文件权限配置。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1325"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:11.993","remediation":"立即修复 SAS System 5.18 安装目录及启动文件的权限配置，确保目录权限设置为 755（drwxr-xr-x），启动文件权限设置为 644（-rw-r--r--），仅允许管理员（SYSTEM/ROOT）拥有写入权限。同时移除不必要的世界可写（world-writable）权限位，并定期审计文件权限变更。如条件允许，升级到 SAS System 6.0 及以上版本以彻底解决权限问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/c-19.shtml","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7261","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1325.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1325","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1325.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1325.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jm5h-qhv5-56m7/GHSA-jm5h-qhv5-56m7.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1325.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001024.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--b9213ca3-14e3-4d16-a7ae-ead8dd18b297.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1041.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1040","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1040.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1323","title":"Symantec Norton AntiVirus NAVIEG及NAVMSE 管理员密码明文存储漏洞","description":"Norton AntiVirus for Internet Email Gateways (NAVIEG) 1.0.1.7及之前版本与Norton AntiVirus for MS Exchange (NAVMSE) 1.5及之前版本存在敏感信息明文存储漏洞。管理员密码以明文形式存储于NAVIEG的navieg.ini配置文件中以及NAVMSE的ModifyPassword注册表项中。本地攻击者可通过读取上述文件或注册表项获取管理员密码，进而获得系统管理权限。该漏洞影响范围较广，利用条件低，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1323"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-04-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:11.737","remediation":"立即升级 NAVIEG 至 1.0.1.8 或更高版本，升级 NAVMSE 至 1.6 或更高版本。如无法升级，手动设置 navieg.ini 文件 NTFS 权限为仅管理员可读，并通过注册表编辑器将 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Symantec\\NAVMSE\\ModifyPassword 项的权限限制为仅管理员可访问，防止非授权用户读取明文密码。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92370067416739&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1323.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1323","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1323.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1323.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hwj6-4xgp-2fx7/GHSA-hwj6-4xgp-2fx7.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x85000/84469/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1323.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8358776d7db47304e3a87c0f78eff81411ac0e47/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1040.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1039","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1039.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1320","title":"Novell NetWare 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Novell NetWare 3.x 及早期版本存在本地权限提升漏洞。本地攻击者可通过伪造数据包（packet spoofing）方式利用该漏洞，获取目标系统更高权限。该漏洞影响 Novell NetWare 3.x 及更早版本，攻击者需具备本地访问权限方可利用，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。建议用户升级至不受影响的版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1320"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:11.360","remediation":"升级至 NetWare 4.x 或更高版本，该版本引入 NCP 分组签名机制。如在 3.x 环境无法升级，可在 AUTOEXEC.NCF 中设置 `SET NCP PACKET SIGNATURE OPTION = 3`，强制要求所有 NCP 请求进行数字签名，防止伪造 NCP 分组实施权限提升。同时建议在交换机上启用端口安全（Port Security）和 DHCP Snooping，限制局域网内的 ARP 欺骗与分组注入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/d-01.shtml","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7213.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1320.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1320","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5c