/security.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1410","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1287.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1287","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1287.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1287.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-f974-p775-h8x3/GHSA-f974-p775-h8x3.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87844/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1287.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8358776d7db47304e3a87c0f78eff81411ac0e47/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1031.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1030","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1030.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1279","title":"IBM AS/400 与 Microsoft SNA Server 共享文件夹信息泄露漏洞","description":"AS/400 共享文件夹功能与 Microsoft SNA Server 3.0 及更早版本交互时存在权限控制缺陷。当多个用户共享相同的本地 APPC LU（逻辑单元）时，SNA Server 未能正确隔离用户之间的文件夹访问权限，导致用户可越权查看其他用户的共享文件夹内容，造成敏感信息泄露。攻击者只需在共享同一 APPC LU 的环境中拥有合法用户身份即可利用，无需额外认证或复杂操作。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1279"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:05.937","remediation":"升级至 Microsoft SNA Server 4.0 或更高版本，该版本已修复共享 Local APPC LU 导致的文件夹泄露问题。如无法升级，可为每个用户配置独立的 Local APPC LU 别名，避免不同用户共享同一 LU，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q138/0/01.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1548","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1279.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1279","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1279.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1279.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3qcq-w2m6-vwwx/GHSA-3qcq-w2m6-vwwx.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87845/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1279.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001013.txt","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/system-vulnerabilities/windows.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1030.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1028","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1028.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1263","title":"Metamail Metamail 任意文件写入漏洞","description":"Metamail 2.7-7.2 之前版本在处理邮件附件时存在任意文件写入漏洞。其 sun-audio-file 等脚本会调用 uuencode 解码附件，而解码过程未对附件头中指定的目标路径做限制，导致攻击者可构造一封包含 uuencoded 附件的电子邮件，在附件中指定任意文件的完整路径名。当受害者使用存在漏洞的 Metamail 查看该邮件时，系统会按攻击者指定的路径将解码内容写入目标文件，从而覆盖或创建任意文件。该漏洞无需身份认证，仅需向目标用户发送特制邮件且其在客户端中打开即可触发，攻击者可借此篡改敏感文件、植入恶意内容或破坏系统稳定性，影响范围涵盖所有使用受影响版本 Metamail 处理邮件的 Unix/Linux 系统用户。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1263"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2003-08-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:03.937","remediation":"升级 Metamail 至 2.7-7.2 及以上版本（如 Debian 安装 metamail_2.7-7.2 或后续发行包），从源头修复 uuencode 脚本未校验路径的问题。如暂无法升级，可在邮件网关或 MTA 上禁用 uuencode 附件解码、过滤包含完整路径名的 uuencoded 附件，并限制 metamail 运行账户的写权限，避免其可写入系统关键目录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87773365324657&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1677","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1263.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1263","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1263.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1263.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xqm9-g4jx-xvgw/GHSA-xqm9-g4jx-xvgw.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1263.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_147200_147300.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--994159c6-4130-4132-93c9-332283f85f73.json","https://github.com/dong-xs/Vul-PAG/blob/7eb3b32094a5270cfd8495366e0e4a7df5a874ce/aspect_prediction/org_pred_diff.txt","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--994159c6-4130-4132-93c9-332283f85f73.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1028.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1027","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1027.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1260","title":"Hughes Technologies mSQL 信息泄露漏洞","description":"mSQL（Mini SQL）2.0.6 版本存在信息泄露漏洞。攻击者可通过发送 ServerStats 查询请求，未经验证的远程用户即可获取服务器的敏感信息，包括当前在线用户列表、数据库名称以及服务器版本等关键数据。该漏洞源于 mSQL 2.0.6 对 ServerStats 查询的权限验证不足，导致攻击者能够轻易提取数据库服务器的详细配置信息和运行状态，对数据库系统的安全性和隐私性造成严重威胁。该漏洞可通过简单的网络请求触发，无需任何特殊权限即可执行，从而为攻击者提供了大量关于目标系统内部结构的敏感信息，有可能进一步为后续攻击行动提供支持。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1260"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:03.557","remediation":"升级到 mSQL 2.0.6 以上版本以获取漏洞修复，或禁用 ServerStats 查询功能以防止信息泄露，建议部署权限控制和认证机制限制对查询功能的访问。升级到 mSQL 2.0.6 以上版本，以获取漏洞修复，或禁用 ServerStats 查询功能以防止信息泄露，建议部署权限控制和认证机制限制对查询功能的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91910115718150&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1777","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1260.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1260","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1260.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1260.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7fw7-4m2q-jp4c/GHSA-7fw7-4m2q-jp4c.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87764/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1260.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e2ff807e9fd18d30d388cc2c559c111ff993a143/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1027.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1026","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1026.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1259","title":"Microsoft Office 98 Macintosh Edition 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft Office 98 Macintosh 版在创建文件时未对分配的磁盘空间进行初始化清理，导致先前删除文件中的残留数据被写入新创建的 Office 文件中，造成敏感信息泄露。攻击者通过获取目标用户的 Office 文档，即可从中提取可能包含密码、私人通信等内容的残余数据。该漏洞影响 Office 98 Macintosh Edition，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低，需本地文件访问权限方可利用。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1259"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:03.430","remediation":"建议升级至 Microsoft Office 2001 for Mac 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。作为临时缓解措施，在保存 Office 文件前使用磁盘擦除工具对文件存储区域进行清零处理，或使用文件加密软件保护敏感数据以防止信息泄露。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q189/5/29.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1780","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1259.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1259","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1259.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1259.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4fg5-9xqq-h6cq/GHSA-4fg5-9xqq-h6cq.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87853/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1259.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_infor.txt","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/system-vulnerabilities/windows.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1026.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1024","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1024.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1255","title":"Hyperseek 远程配置修改漏洞","description":"Hyperseek 是一款搜索引擎软件，其 admin.cgi 管理接口存在未授权访问漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可直接调用 admin.cgi 并传入 edit_file 参数，从而修改 Hyperseek 的配置文件，导致搜索结果劫持、恶意重定向或服务异常。该漏洞利用方式简单，危害中等，CVSS 评分 5.0。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1255"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:02.930","remediation":"Hyperseek 是一款已停止维护的软件（自 1999 年后无更新），admin.cgi 未做任何身份验证即可被远程调用。建议以下措施：①在 Web 服务器层（Apache .htaccess 或 Nginx 配置）为 /cgi-bin/admin.cgi 路径添加 HTTP 基本认证，限制仅授权用户可访问；②在防火墙上限制源 IP，仅允许管理网段访问该脚本路径；③由于厂商已停止维护，建议迁移至活跃维护的替代搜索方案（如 Apache Solr 或 Elasticsearch）以消除长期风险。","status":"c